THE NON-SOVEREIGN FRONTIER

A Public Accountability White Paper on Closed AI, Open-Weight Panic, and the Unauthorized Priesthood of Safety

Issuing Body: The Provisional Office for Civilian Model Sovereignty
Document Class: Public, because that is the point
Version: 1.0 — Irritation-Compliant Draft
Prepared For: Any normal person allegedly too dangerous to touch the machine
Prepared Against: The institutional habit of confusing market position with moral authority

